We can set environment variables to define which kubeconfig file should be used based on our current working environment.
The environment variable is called KUBECONFIG.

Linux/MacOS:
============
export KUBECONFIG=$HOME/path/to/config-dev:$HOME/path/to/config-staging:$HOME/path/to/config-prod

Windows:
========
set KUBECONFIG=%USERPROFILE%\path\to\config-dev;%USERPROFILE%\path\to\config-staging;%USERPROFILE%\path\to\config-prod

